SubjectAdministrator of the Government of British Columbia
PrecisAppointment to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of BRITISH COLUMBIA (1) the Hon. GEOFFREY R.J. GAUL from March 9 to 13, 2015, inclusive, and from September 14 to 18, 2015, inclusive; and (2) the Hon. ROBERT T.C. JOHNSTON from March 16 to 21, 2015, inclusive.
